t: How much does New Balance pay Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone? All about the Olympic champion's multi-million dollar deal with the brand
s: October 26, 2024 - Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone's dominant performance at the Paris Olympics solidified her status as a top athlete. In addition to her athletic prowess, she has been a brand ambassador for New Balance since the age of 19, earning an annual salary of $1.5 million.
